page.title: 21Pubs,Garages in Sherburn In Elmet
page.content: there are still five pubs in sherburn in elmet only two now do meals on a lunchtime the oddfellows and the wheatsheaf , no discos anymore in the red bear as it is a sam smiths which do not have music licences.there are no garages left in sherburn in elmet that sell petrol / deisel and only cliff motors left of the named ones doing repairs.
